HEADWORD: loincloth
<hw>loincloth</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A cloth covering for the loins,
worn around the hips; -- sometimes worn in tropical areas as the only
article of clothing.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> breechcloth, breechclout, G-string.</syn>⟦br⟧
